<p class="input_wrapper">
  <input value="3" type="checkbox" class="skipValidation" <%= value==3 ? "checked='checked'" : "" %> <%= readonly ? "disabled=\"disabled\"" : ""%>></input>
  <span>Interactions with the learning object <b>are meaningful</b> and permit the user to have a much greater understanding of the concept/topic than he/she would have if she used a text based medium.</span>
